WEBVTT

00:00:30.520 --> 00:00:32.000
Ajoyib g’oya, to’g’rimi?

00:00:32.880 --> 00:00:34.096
Nima o'xshamasligi
mumkin?

00:00:34.120 --> 00:00:35.640
(Kulgu)

00:00:36.400 --> 00:00:38.456
Xo’sh, dastlab biz 40 kishi edik,

00:00:38.480 --> 00:00:40.936
va men har gal kimnidir ismini
eshitishim bilan

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:42.760
shodligimdan uree deb yuborardim.

00:00:43.280 --> 00:00:45.776
So’ng 20 kishi qoldi,

00:00:45.800 --> 00:00:47.576
keyin 10 kishi,

00:00:47.600 --> 00:00:48.960
undan keyin 5 kishi…

00:00:49.560 --> 00:00:50.936
nihoyat 3 kishi.

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:52.160
Va ulardan biri men edim.

00:00:52.720 --> 00:00:54.320
Yoqimli so’zlar
ulashish to’xtadi.

00:00:55.560 --> 00:00:57.600
Men o’sha daqiqada yig’layotgan edim.

00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:00.616
Ustozning hafsalasi pir bo’lib,